{
  "stem": "10768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I will prepare whatever I can do to prepare to make a very merry Christmas for them-- decorate, cook, make whatever you make, the dinner.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But please, for Christmas Day, for Christmas Day, I would like to have another two days of furlough to go to-- because somebody who survived the war is near Praga, which is about 20 kilometers away, or 25 approximately.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did I find where this is?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the patients that came to us, there were always little shootings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they came and I was inquiring, where is this number of that unit?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where is that unit?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said, I think it's in Rembertow near Praga, which was on our side, on the Russian side of the river Vistula.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you went over the Vistula, Warsaw was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Christmas Day, we had another Jew which was called [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Brandt. ?] He originally lived in Praga, but apparently decide-- anyhow, I don't know if Praga was divided also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I will go too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the hospital was good enough to give me a motor vehicle already, not a horse and buggy, but a little pickup truck and that Brandt went with me and the chauffeur went with me.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came to the unit on Christmas Day and found Leon Finver from our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, I was there-- I don't remember if I was there overnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably yes, or maybe no because then Brandt also wanted to go and look.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, he didn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was heartbroken.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- he was in a depressed mood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we came back to our hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That pickup, the chauffeur brought us back.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
